events.name: Cloud Study Jam - Machine Learning (Beginner + Advanced)
events.description:
The wait for Cloud Study Jams end for Mumbai !!

Want to get started on the Google Cloud services, but don't know where to begin? Join us for our Cloud Study Jam!

Get official Google training, a $55+ value, free of charge. Together we'll work through several Google Cloud labs. You will get hands-on experience with the Cloud Console, Kubernetes, Security, IoT on Cloud, and Machine Learning on Google Cloud platform.

Then after our live session, you will have free access to more labs you can finish at home. Complete all labs in the quest and earn a Google-hosted badge for your online profile, and additional 30 days access to the training platform to compete any labs you want

We are organizing the study jam for 3 tracks - Machine Learning, Kubernetes and Cloud Services.

We are starting off the season with hottest topic Machine Learning. The event will be conducted on 2 Saturday back to back taking you through basic as well as advanced topics.

Bring a laptop (fully charged, will have limited power sockets).
The labs will run on all of the latest versions of the popular browsers.
For the best experience, make sure your laptop has Firefox or Chrome installed.

Register yourself here!!
http://bit.ly/GCDCMumbai_MLStudyJam

Note:
RSVP through meetup is not applicable and registration is mandatory using above link.

events.name: Cloud Study Jam - Kubernetes
events.description:
Agenda for our next StudyJam Event...
======================================

Kubernetes (K8S) is the most popular container orchestration system and it was designed specifically with Google Cloud Platform integration in mind. This study jam will teach you the practical skills needed for integrating container orchestration into your own workflow -

Agenda:
1. Introduction to Docker/Containers.
2. Understanding Kubernetes (K8S).
3. Orchestrating the Cloud with K8S.
4. Continuous Delivery with Jenkins on K8S.
5. Distributed Load testing using K8S.
6. Running dedicated Game servers on GKE.

Register yourself here!!

events.name: Google Cloud Next '19 Extended, Mumbai
events.description:
After running a series of Cloud study jams, We are back with our next Meetup – “Google Cloud Next ’19 Extended”.

Google Cloud Next took place from 9th to 11th April in San Francisco. It included many exciting announcements about Google Cloud’s products that will be releasing/released this year.

Come join us on 18th May,2019 where we discuss about announcements from Cloud Next'19.

We'll be covering exciting topics like
1. Mobility and it's Business Use Cases by Deesha Vora
2. Cloud Run by Vaibhav Malpani
3. ML in Production by Arun Kutty
4. Anthos and Major announcements from Next'19 by Dharmesh
Followed by lunch and networking.

Note: RSVP through meetup is mandatory and would be considered as ticket

Special thanks to our Venue partner - 91springboard 74 Techno Park, Andheri East,Mumbai
